{
  "texts": [
    "Attacks that correspond to the stages of GenAI application development are described in more detail below.Training-time attacks.",
    "The TRAINING STAGE for GenAI often consists of two distinct stages: foundation model PRE-TRAINING and model FINE-TUNING.",
    "This pattern exists for generative image models, text models, audio models, and multimodal models, among others.",
    "Since foundation models are most effective when trained on large datasets, it has become common to scrape data from a wide range of public sources.",
    "This makes foundation models especially susceptible to POISONING ATTACKS, in which an adversary controls a subset of the training data."
  ]
}